@tatianashp
TensorFlow cannot solve the problem that two features hash collision when the we set fixed hash_bucket_size in current TensorFlow version.
I think this is a "feature request". We need an API without the parameter “hash_bucket_size”, and its size dynamic grows when a new feature is coming.

